::Havoc::

Havoc climbs out of the CR tank, repaired. He had one pit of a 
headache. Havoc growls. He was going to kill that Maximal next time 
he saw him.

Walking back to the cargo bay, Havoc almost crashes into Vlad before 
he sees him. He jumps back, his hand near his gun.

"I see you're out of your pod," Havoc comments, watching Vlad 
carefully.
